{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User\\loyalty-app","sessionId":"621054d0-26c3-408a-b97e-5923cbd83f77","version":"2.1.56","gitBranch":"HEAD","agentId":"a32e708a2a53144e3","slug":"squishy-launching-crayon","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 33: Final Polish + CI/CD for a loyalty card app.\n\n**Working directory:** C:\\Users\\User\\loyalty-app\n\n**What to do:**\n\n### 1. Create EAS config for mobile app\n\nCreate `apps/mobile/eas.json`:\n```json\n{\n  \"build\": {\n    \"preview\": {\n      \"distribution\": \"internal\",\n      \"ios\": { \"simulator\": true }\n    },\n    \"production\": {\n      \"autoIncrement\": true\n    }\n  },\n  \"submit\": {\n    \"production\": {\n      \"ios\": {\n        \"appleId\": \"YOUR_APPLE_ID\",\n        \"ascAppId\": \"YOUR_ASC_APP_ID\"\n      },\n      \"android\": {\n        \"serviceAccountKeyPath\": \"./play-store-key.json\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Create GitHub Actions CI\n\nCreate `.github/workflows/ci.yml`:\n```yaml\nname: CI\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main]\n\njobs:\n  lint-typecheck:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: pnpm/action-setup@v4\n        with:\n          version: 9\n      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: 20\n          cache: pnpm\n      - run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n      - run: pnpm turbo lint typecheck\n\n  build-dashboard:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: lint-typecheck\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: pnpm/action-setup@v4\n        with:\n          version: 9\n      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: 20\n          cache: pnpm\n      - run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n      - run: pnpm --filter dashboard build\n        env:\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL: ${{ secrets.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL }}\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY: ${{ secrets.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY }}\n```\n\n### 3. Create a simple README at the project root\n\nCreate `loyalty-app/README.md`:\n```markdown\n# Loyalty App\n\nA B2B2C digital loyalty platform — mobile app (consumer) + web dashboard (merchant) + Supabase backend.\n\n## Structure\n\n- `apps/mobile` — React Native (Expo) consumer app\n- `apps/dashboard` — Next.js merchant dashboard\n- `packages/shared` — Shared TypeScript types\n- `supabase/` — Database migrations + Edge Functions\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Prerequisites\n- Node.js 20+\n- pnpm 9+\n- Supabase CLI (optional, for local dev)\n\n### Install\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Development\n```bash\n# Dashboard\npnpm --filter dashboard dev\n\n# Mobile\ncd apps/mobile && npx expo start\n```\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nCopy `.env.example` files in `apps/dashboard/` and configure:\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`\n- `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`\n- `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET`\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **Mobile:** React Native + Expo SDK 54, Expo Router, Zustand, i18next\n- **Dashboard:** Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui\n- **Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Edge Functions, Storage)\n- **Payments:** Stripe\n- **Push:** Expo Notifications\n```\n\n### 4. Commit\n\n```bash\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"chore: add CI/CD pipeline, EAS config, and README\"\n```\n\n**Important:**\n- Create the `.github/workflows/` directory structure\n- The README should be simple and accurate\n- Do NOT skip the commit\n"},"uuid":"094177ce-d158-4dc1-8857-49350b1b5f1c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:23:45.452Z"}
