{"parentUuid":"6c1370d9-2680-4e62-9333-24b4bf3c1e98","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User\\loyalty-app","sessionId":"621054d0-26c3-408a-b97e-5923cbd83f77","version":"2.1.56","gitBranch":"HEAD","agentId":"a32e708a2a53144e3","slug":"squishy-launching-crayon","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018Am7EUZqnNQ2t6ELNXThqj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011AmFrPe3Fr7JKpeDZH2gaY","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"C:/Users/User/loyalty-app/README.md","content":"# Loyalty App\n\nA B2B2C digital loyalty platform — mobile app (consumer) + web dashboard (merchant) + Supabase backend.\n\n## Structure\n\n- `apps/mobile` — React Native (Expo) consumer app\n- `apps/dashboard` — Next.js merchant dashboard\n- `packages/shared` — Shared TypeScript types\n- `supabase/` — Database migrations + Edge Functions\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Prerequisites\n- Node.js 20+\n- pnpm 9+\n- Supabase CLI (optional, for local dev)\n\n### Install\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Development\n```bash\n# Dashboard\npnpm --filter dashboard dev\n\n# Mobile\ncd apps/mobile && npx expo start\n```\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nCopy `.env.example` files in `apps/dashboard/` and configure:\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`\n- `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`\n- `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET`\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **Mobile:** React Native + Expo SDK 54, Expo Router, Zustand, i18next\n- **Dashboard:** Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui\n- **Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Edge Functions, Storage)\n- **Payments:** Stripe\n- **Push:** Expo Notifications\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":461,"cache_read_input_tokens":18668,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":461},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CYVtNscVLzhXs6